p(style=`margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.foreground};`) Hi{{ if .Subscriber.FirstName }} {{ .Subscriber.FirstName }}{{ else }} there{{ end }},
p(style=`margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.foreground};`) Thanks for subscribing. One more click confirms that you want updates from #{sitename}.
p(style=`margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.foreground};`) Expect occasional notes on software engineering, growth experiments and whatever else is worth sharing.
p(style=`margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.foreground};`)
    a(href="{{ .OptinURL }}", style=`display:inline-block; padding:14px 20px; background-color:${theme.accent}; border:1px solid ${theme.accent}; color:${theme.background}; text-decoration:none; font-size:16px; line-height:1.2; font-weight:bold;`) Confirm subscription
p(style=`margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.muted};`)
    | If the button does not work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
    br
    a(href="{{ .OptinURL }}", style=`color:${theme.accent}; text-decoration:none; word-break:break-all;`) {{ .OptinURL }}
p(style=`margin:0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.7; color:${theme.muted};`) If this was not you, you can safely ignore this message.
